title: Request not found. You do not have access to request #0. It may have been solved or deleted.
body: What does this mean? i tried to open ticket and i get this message.

replies.body: It looks like the tickets you're trying to pull up have been solved out for a little over a year now, so that might be why they are no longer pulling up. Try [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or possibly loading the ticket form in a private/incognito window and let me know if either of those work.
